How does ChatGPT handle multiple languages?
text:
Im trying to understand how chatgpt works and how it handles different languages. Can it use what it has learned in one language (by being trained with data in that language) to answer or talk in another language? Or the responses in one language are completly independent from ones in another language?

I kinda understand how it tokenizes an input and use embeddings to compress and decompress. But a token created in one language correlates to one of the same meaning in another language?

Thanks.
